data.description: Welcome to your dream home at Flat Creek Reserve! This custom 4-bed, 4-bath haven boasts elegance with hardwood floors throughout the living spaces, coffered ceiling and judges paneling in the formal dining room, and a breathtaking stone fireplace in the living room. The primary bedroom is spacious and has a custom storage system in the large closet. The primary bathroom features a tile shower and separate vanities. Upstairs, the fourth bedroom comes complete with its own private full bathroom.  Step outside to discover the beauty of a private lake, a screened-in back patio, and a wooden porch. The living room seamlessly connects to the outdoors through double doors leading to the back porch, which can be shaded by a retractable awning. Experience convenience with automated blinds in the living room and eat-in kitchen, allowing you to control the ambiance at the touch of a button. This home is not just a residence; it's a sanctuary where luxury meets comfort, and every detail has been carefully crafted for your enjoyment.
